Did you ever listen to a song over and over again, each time focusing on a
different instrument, first guitar, then bass, then drums?  You can do
something similar with characters on Joss's shows, especially in an
episode like The Body.  This last time I concentrated on Tara, especially
in the dorm scene.  Notice her reaction when Willow first snipes at Anya
